      • addArchangel

        public java.lang.String addArchangel(java.lang.String pname,
                                     java.lang.String pphoto,
                                     java.lang.String ppower,
                                     java.lang.String ppray,
                                     java.lang.String pcolor,
                                     double psize,
                                     java.lang.String pessence,
                                     int plight,
                                     int pday,
                                     java.lang.String pmonth,
                                     Candle cand,
                                     Date date)
        This method adds an archangel to the legion
        pre: The objects candle and date must be created.
        post: The archangel has been added.
        Parameters:
        pname - Name of the archangel. pname != null && pname != "".
        pphoto - Photo of the archangel. pphoto != null && pphoto != "".
        ppower - Power of the archangel. ppower != null && ppower != "".
        ppray - Pray of the archangel. ppray != null && ppray != "".
        pcolor - Color of the candle. pcolor != null && pcolor != "".
        psize - Size of the candle. psize != null && psize != "".
        pessence - Essence of the candle. pessence != null && pessence != "".
        plight - Light degree of the candle. plight != null && plight != "".
        pday - Day of the date. pday != null && pday != "".
        pmonth - Month of the date. pmonth != null && pmonth != "".
        cand - Candle object of the archangel. cand != null.
        date - Date object of the archangel. date != null.
        Returns:
        msg Indicating if the archangel was registered or not. msg != null && msg != "".
